### list al the messages

GET http://localhost:3000/messages

### get a message by id

GET http://localhost:3000/messages/1

### create a message

POST http://localhost:3000/messages
content-type: application/json

{
  "content": "hello world"
}

### create a message invalid content

POST http://localhost:3000/messages
content-type: application/json

{
  "content": 123
}